args: Well, ain't that a real flat soda!\nWhy's everybody got to hotfoot it\nthe moment they see me?
You there! Pal! You a swordsman?
I knew it! You look like a cat what\nreally knows his way around a blade.
In that case, I challenge you to a duel.\n....C'mon, ya gotta! Ya just gotta!
Uh, boss? Don't wanna worry ya or\nnothin', but I think that's Yachiyo.
I take it that's not a good thing?
I've heard tales. Apparently she's been\nwanderin' the area askin' everybody\nshe sees what to duel her.
That big side'a beef next to you really\nknows his onions. Now draw your blade!
I have no reason to fight you.
Oh, I'll give you a reason, pal...
I'm gonna win a thousand duels\nand become the strongest warrior\nin the entire world!
I wasn't aware that was the process.
My grandpappy taught me the art of the\nsword, and he says it's true as a new\nfence on an open range!
Er, I'll assume that's very true.\nStill, it's quite the lofty goal.

I've been traveling the world giving
palookas the business for a while now.
But once I achieved my 900th victory,
everything went goldfish bellies.
Sure, but that's small potatoes!\nI gotta defeat a thousand of 'em\nor it don't mean squat.
But now everybody hits the skids\nthe moment I show my face in town.
Hell, I'd probably turn and run from some\ncrazy swordswoman who took out nine\nhundred fighters before gettin' to me.
I ain't never gonna be the strongest\nif no else is willing to put up their dukes.
That's why I need you to fight me!
Now come on, already! Stop being such\na damp rug and let's do this thing!
I told you, I'm not fighting you.
But you just said you'd fight\nif I gave ya a reason!
You gave me YOUR reason for fighting.
That's all well and good for you,\nbut I still have no reason to fight.
Look, I'm older than you, yeah?\nSo respect your elders and fight!
If I can't get nobody to dance, I'm gonna\nlose all my moxie. And then? ...Poof!\nMy goal will be six feet under!
I think we've taken this conversation\nabout as far as it's gonna go.\nLet's split, {player_name}.
Wait just a sec. {player_name}?\nI know that handle!
You're the seventh heir to the throne!\nThe prince what's always fightin'\nfor the sake of others!
Um, yeah. That's me, I guess.
You've got plenty of angry joes who want\nyour head, yeah? And that means I'LL\nhave plenty of angry joes to fight!
It's an endless supply of goons!
Now hold on! Ya can't just—
Did someone drop you on yer head?\nIt won't be ten minutes before this\nlady's challengin' ya to a duel again!
And if I leave her alone, she'll challenge\nsomeone else instead.
Tsk! You really are a soft touch.

So then, Yachiyo, you're welcome to
come with us—but I have a condition.
Until you duel me, you're not allowed
to duel anyone else. Are we agreed?
Well, that's a real raw steak of a deal!\n...Still, I suppose it beats pounding the\npavement lookin' for mopes to fight.
